# Read the Spec Before Coding

Before changing `web/src/` or `scripts/`, read the matching spec from `specs/README.md`.

| Code | Spec |
| :--- | :--- |
| `scripts/clean_bbg_export.py` | `specs/data-pipeline.md` |
| `scripts/phase1_build.py` | `specs/signals-backtest.md` |
| `web/src/**` | `specs/web-dashboard.md` |

If the spec and code disagree, fix the spec or the code immediately — do not silently diverge.
